</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00312/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一块蛋糕，内部被形态类似的琼脂糖凝胶取代，在生物食用后可使该生物的随机染色体或线粒体内DNA片段（通常长度在0.5kb~4.1kb之内）变异且强制该异常变异序列表达。该琼脂糖凝胶核酸检测为阴性。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>广州市黄埔区██大酒店一包间内。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>已被转移至Site-CN-██分子生物学实验室作进一步研究。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>“一个因为超级细菌感染，万古霉素无效，死于败血症的，一个因为胰岛素分泌过量低血糖死的，还有一个死于休克后，尸检报告说在组织内检出大量金属零件的……”——Dr.Xenon</em><br />
<em>“比CRISPR-Cas9好用多了，如果不是因为这该死的随机性。”——Dr.Neon</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00312" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00312" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00312-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6213424); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6213424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180084" alt="ChroIridium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6213424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6213424); return false;">ChroIridium</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1594650129 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">13 Jul 2020 14:22</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00482/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一段会让相关描述变敷衍的文字<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>地球<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>忘了<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>就这样</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00482" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00482" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00482-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/link-boundaryless" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7126666); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7126666&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180084" alt="Link Boundaryless" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7126666)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/link-boundaryless" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7126666); return false;">Link Boundaryless</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1608295524 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">18 Dec 2020 12:45</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00419/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">项目描述</span>：</strong>一副由<span style="font-size:x-large;">████公司</span>生产的<span style="font-size:x-large;">███眼镜</span>，会使<span style="font-size:x-large;">佩戴者</span>认为其所看到的<span style="font-size:x-large;">文字</span>中的<span style="font-size:x-large;">名词部分</span>比<span style="font-size:x-large;">其他部分</span>要大一些。<br />
<strong>回收<span style="font-size:x-large;">日期</span>：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收<span style="font-size:x-large;">地点</span>：</strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">████公司专卖店</span>。<br />
<strong>当前<span style="font-size:x-large;">状态</span>：</strong>存放于Dr.K的<span style="font-size:x-large;">办公室</span>内。<br />
<strong><span style="font-size:x-large;">笔记</span>：</strong><em>确实是大<strong>亿</strong>些。&#8212;Dr.K</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00419" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00419" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00419-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kaster-k" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6606914); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6606914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180084" alt="kaster-k" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6606914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kaster-k" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6606914); return false;">kaster-k</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1601610342 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">02 Oct 2020 03:45</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00187/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一篇拉丁文写就的莎草纸手稿，内容为证明π是一个绝对正规数的证明，计算得出手稿中的“π”等于当前定义的π的两倍。手稿中的证明过程逻辑自洽而运用了当前未知的数学公理，任何完整研读并掌握手稿内容的个体将会表现出对数学家Leonhard Euler及其研究成果崇拜和原教旨主义，并否认任何Leonhard Euler死后数学进展的合理性。此效应仅持续24小时。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>2020/04/15<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>基金会文物研究与保管部<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>保存于Site-CN-75的文物研究与保管部<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>首次发现项目是于4月15日的Site-CN-75，当时文物研究与保管部的成员就应将哪一条欧拉公式纹在自己身上而发生的争吵。</p>
<p>于9月18日，基金会文物研究与保管部将<tt>“e<sup>iπ</sup> +1 = 0”</tt>作为部门标志。</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00187" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00187" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00187-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3167340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180084" alt="Yoghurt-rescuer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3167340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;">Yoghurt-rescuer</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1589256888 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">12 May 2020 04:14</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
    
